articles.title: Lifeguard drops prosthetic leg to rescue driver of sinking SUV
articles.description: An off-duty lifeguard in New Jersey is being hailed as a hero after he shed his prosthetic leg to jump into Newark Bay and rescue the driver of an SUV that plunged into the water.
articles.content:
